{"tid":1679142,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解武器要普及化同多樣化？","createTime":"2019-10-28T04:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:06:01.000Z","uid":260650,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"aac29c65ac29c2ba0513dd244bd44e8d4cd64abc","tid":1679142,"uid":260650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"我好耐之前已經講人力弓<br />\n煙霧滅蟲彈呢D<br />\n有左，之後點<br />\n武器普及化反而差左<br />\n甚至係惡化<br />\n<br />\n無錯高火力武器有酒有酸有盾係進步左<br />\n<br />\n但係大家唔係好明<br />\n數量先係步兵戰基本<br />\n你10個人用拳頭打死一個左輪<br />\n你100個人用弓可能勝到10個步槍<br />\n你1000個人打10部坦克亦唔係假<br />\n<br />\n武器其實唔使好勁<br />\n你有100支pocket shot分比100人比起1個人有100支氣油彈勁<br />\n<br />\n同樣防具唔一定要Full load<br />\n頭盔？無咪包一堆毛巾防直擊先lo<br />\n盾？無咪整發泡膠加燒烤網加玻璃膠二夾一lo<br />\n口罩？無咪用濕水毛巾包面lo<br />\n民兵優勢其實除左機動同隱藏<br />\n仲有數量同成本<br />\n將入場費set到鬼咁高把撚<br />\n大家係要阿叔伯母女仔男仔都可以輕鬆用，輕鬆放棄既武器同防具<br />\n務求係拉多D人入水，由淺入深<br />\n之後成本分散到700萬人身上，政府除非all kill，一係倒台<br />\n<br />\n如果阿婆阿伯都知道打popo好容易好好玩，甚至仲可以同孫仔同場較量，一比身手，果一日popo唔使指意出到狗屋<br />\n<br />\n真心<br />\n勁D<br />\n咪做弓，投石機，各種魔法lo<br />\n唔得<br />\n咪pocket shot<br />\n再原始D，咪出人力弓比阿叔玩下lo<br />\n都唔得？投石索lo<br />\n射唔中又如何？阿叔開心參與完，開始叫阿伯<br />\n阿伯玩完自製盾，學到手藝，1個10蚊，你又開心佢又開心<br />\n阿婆見到仲開心，開始落街賣自製弓，100蚊支，好過收紙皮<br />\n到時，就真係全民抗爭<br />\n<br />\n中共倒台<br />\n港共遭殃"},{"pid":"7b1e66c2c585489e8fb433a9944f10184b8f7384","tid":1679142,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好剩係懲罰出名嘅黃店？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675556</a>"},{"pid":"bdb07abfeda08a56b1903c8f1869028938f903c1","tid":1679142,"uid":80763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5156612ca6341d82a8874bdbb7776c1cf1ec7e","tid":1679142,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=922a150b\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=06c2e973\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=996b7d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"b5f2bf82443cb65bd4ae3b469d05875be0679095","tid":1679142,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"再普通咪掟下雞蛋<br />\nPopo啲裝咁靚"},{"pid":"b46c4946ccebeb760b5bf8f3e442cd60c7ef7d8e","tid":1679142,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab94cb42d9600f0cf0ade32b24eb911e7cc6a48b","tid":1679142,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港民調，追蹤長期民意，做份國際文宣，話比全世界聽 5毛大軍不代表香港人<br />\n<br />\n連登post: 鍾庭耀教授都企左出來....你仲做冷氣軍師??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n眾籌link: <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=wmdQs5dGAEixecl6soOD56VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=996b7d68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"8f13508ed9099b5bb778d605cc576d959406eba7","tid":1679142,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b0ad73964b0dd02cdcfbdcc41ad6a092726ddf0","tid":1679142,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n次次見到圍觀屌既人多<br />\n行動救人既人少<br />\n<br />\n雖然設身處地諗就會明<br />\n如果我立即撲上去出手<br />\n會唔會無人響應？<br />\n會唔會得我突左出黎做埋犧牲品？<br />\n<br />\n之前有巴打些牙左條片<br />\n講到其實集體行動上 第二三四五個參與者都好重要<br />\n只要真係開始人多去做 <br />\n自然件事就會變得合理化同大眾化<br />\n<br />\n或者守法守規則對香港人黎講已經根深蒂固<br />\n不過最近開始多左上年紀既手足係前線<br />\n我相信全民勇武指日可待<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93adb0541c76de3480e8c8d84d88c82acd17e275","tid":1679142,"uid":260650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"無人回我"},{"pid":"b098f281fa810317d68ea9be648595cb8fadb13d","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n和理非一人一支可樂樽都幾過癮"},{"pid":"63c7f6c8e267f4055c60b6fde3820dd8401cda14","tid":1679142,"uid":260650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b098f281fa810317d68ea9be648595cb8fadb13d","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n和理非一人一支可樂樽都幾過癮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"幫我推下啦"},{"pid":"cd45d9a64d736621c28f93110a49a764d3dd08d1","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63c7f6c8e267f4055c60b6fde3820dd8401cda14","tid":1679142,"uid":260650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b098f281fa810317d68ea9be648595cb8fadb13d","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n和理非一人一支可樂樽都幾過癮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"幫我推下啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n睇下班藍絲<br />\n一齊掟磚幾齊心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540bac995387bdbce1a84f25592e2db90f645186","tid":1679142,"uid":231007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20c39c7e9d3e31a25c4b540ea2c3b5c8f67b540c","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dbc4e84420a94eeac32b50b341c4e313b460d7b","tid":1679142,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score